#-------Run pytest-------------
From IDE:
Edit configuartions---  + ---python test---pytest
From Terminal:
Initialize path of the pytest folder
py.test-----all test step by step
py.test –v -----to see more information
py.test –v –s ----to see the console log
py.test  syntax.py –v –s ----to run specific file
py.test -k CreditCard -v –s --- regular expression
py.test -m smoke -v –s ---- tag
